Package: genefunnel
Title: Gene Set Activity Scoring with GeneFunnel
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Emir", "Turkes", email = "emir.turkes@eturkes.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computes sample-wise gene set activity scores from non-negative
    feature-by-sample matrices. Each score combines the observed feature sum
    with a penalty for absolute deviation within the gene set.
